text: Cryptofusus cryptocarinatus is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Fasciolariidae, the spindle snails, the tulip snails and their allies. ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species can be found along New Zealand. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Fasciolariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1956
title: Cryptofusus cryptocarinatus
